  "markup": "\u003Ch2\u003EWho We Are\u003C/h2\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EWe are a team of strategists, designers, and developers united by a shared belief: that technology should serve people, not the other way around. Founded with a focus on meaningful digital outcomes, we have grown into a trusted partner for organisations navigating the complexity of the modern web.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ch2\u003EOur Mission\u003C/h2\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EOur mission is to help businesses build lasting digital experiences. We do this by combining strategic thinking with hands-on craft \u2014 from the first discovery workshop through to long-term support and iteration.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ch2\u003EWhat We Value\u003C/h2\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EClarity\u003C/strong\u003E \u2014 We communicate simply and honestly, even when the subject is complex.\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECuriosity\u003C/strong\u003E \u2014 We ask questions, explore ideas, and never stop learning.\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECraft\u003C/strong\u003E \u2014 We take pride in the quality of what we build and how we build it.\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ECollaboration\u003C/strong\u003E \u2014 The best results come from working closely with our clients, not just for them.\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Ch2\u003EThe Team\u003C/h2\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EWe bring together specialists across strategy, content, design, and engineering. While our skills vary, our commitment to doing great work is something we all share. We are small enough to care and experienced enough to deliver.\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
    </bodyText>
